declarations.name: computeData
declarations.body: fun computeData(value: Int): Int { fun addExtra(extra: Int): Int { return extra + DEFAULT_COUNT } return value * internalData + addExtra(10) }

declarations.name: addExtra
declarations.body: fun addExtra(extra: Int): Int { return extra + DEFAULT_COUNT }}

declarations.name: processData
declarations.body: fun processData(value: Int): Int { return computeData(value) }

declarations.name: displayHelp
declarations.body: fun displayHelp() { val helper = ParserChecker.Helper() println(helper.assist()) }

declarations.name: updateConfig
declarations.body: fun updateConfig(key: String, value: String) { configMap = configMap + (key to value) }

declarations.name: main
declarations.body: fun main() { val parser = ParserChecker.create() println("Processed Data: ${parser.processData(23)}") displayHelp() Configuration.updateConfig("newKey", "newValue") println("Config Updated: ${Configuration.configMap}") println(parser.extensionFunction()) }
